source_code: Donated to the Rubenianum by Karsten Evers (Hans Gerhard Evers' youngest son) in 2019.
Annotation: Donated to the Rubenianum by Karsten Evers (Hans Gerhard Evers' youngest son) in 2019.

Description: Photocopies of pages 110-113 and 168-171 of the publication 'The Making of Rubens', by Svetlana Alpers (1995). In note 5 there is a comment (marked in yellow) on a publication of Evers, mentioning: "Serious questions about Evers's politics during the Second World War explains a general silence about the remarkable intelligence and nuance of his writing."
